pcePcepSessNumReqSentCancelRcvd OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Counter32 MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The number of requests sent on this session that were cancelled by the peer with a PCNtf message.
This might be different than pcePcepSessNumPCNtfRcvd because not all PCNtf messages are used to cancel requests, and a single PCNtf message can cancel multiple requests." ::= { pcePcepSessEntry 35 }
pcePcepSessNumReqSentErrorRcvd OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Counter32 MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The number of requests sent on this session that were rejected by the peer with a PCErr message.
