pcePcepSessNumReqRcvdPendRep OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Counter32 MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The number of requests that have been received on this session for which a response is still pending." ::= { pcePcepSessEntry 41 }
