pcePcepSessNumReqRcvdCancelSent OBJECT-TYPE SYNTAX Counter32 MAX-ACCESS read-only STATUS current DESCRIPTION "The number of requests received on this session that were cancelled by the local PCEP speaker sending a PCNtf message.
